      </userestrict>
      <relatedmaterial id="aspace_de1d9ef42b7fd891373ace5d3a9365aa">
         <head>Related Materials</head>
         <p>Related material: Bernard Bloch papers (MS 1129). Series I: GENERAL FILES, 1936-1965 contains Sturtevant correspondence.</p>
         <p>Associated material: Linguistic Society of America Records, 1896-1998 (C3974), Series FFFF: Edgar H. Sturtevant Correspondence is located at the State Historical Society of Missouri.</p>
         <p>Associated material: Franz Boas Papers, Correspondents S and the Franz Boas Personal and Professional Papers, Series I. Professional correspondence both containing Sturtevant correspondence are located at the American Philosophical Society.</p>
      </relatedmaterial>
